EN: Agriculture is the main source of livelihood for farmers.

ZH: 农业是食品安全的基础。
EN: Agriculture is the foundation of food security.

ZH: 农业的发展需要政府的支持。
EN: The development of agriculture requires support from the government.

ZH: 农业生产有时候会受到天气的影响。
EN: Agricultural production can sometimes be affected by weather conditions.

